website_info.summary: Ironworks Collective, Inc. is a cannabis cultivation and distribution company located in Los Angeles, California. They hold an active adult-use and medicinal cannabis license and operate a cultivation facility. In addition to cannabis products, they also grow and distribute various leafy greens and other produce items.
